text: Atka may refer to: *Atka, Alaska, a city in the United States, on Atka Island **Atka Airport, a public airport in Alaska, United States *Atka, Russia, an urban-type settlement in Magadan Oblast, Russia *Atka Iceport, an iceport in West Antarctica *Atka Island, in the Andreanof Islands **Mount Atka (AKA Korovin Volcano), the highest point of Atka Island *USCGC Southwind (WAGB-280) (USS Atka (AGB-3)), a United States Coast Guard ice breaker
